{"tid":1524541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人對黨鐵既醒覺嚟得太遲","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:39:16.000Z","uid":203508,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"500dfa599c969b91a76e6d7ec9ea270efb46a586","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2007年 兩鐵合併<br />\n2008年 上海地鐵落成<br />\n2009年 港鐵營運既北京地鐵落成<br />\n2009年 深圳地鐵龍華綫全綫開通<br />\n2009年 港鐵投得杭州地鐵營運權及上蓋物業發展權<br />\n2009年 港鐵投得瀋陽地鐵營運權及上蓋物業發展權<br />\n2012年 杭州地鐵落成</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">淨係維基都搵到咁多啦<br />\n唔該各位手足做好資料蒐集<br />\n發完夢唔好搭黨鐵！！</span></span><br />\n中國大陸為港鐵公司業務發展策略的重點，主要集中在城市鐵路的開發及投資，並為中國大陸提供鐵路營運、物業管理及顧問服務[41]。目前，北京港鐵四號綫項目進展暢順，港鐵公司亦為深圳市軌道交通四號綫項目獲得審批作好準備，並繼續在杭州、蘇州、天津及武漢等主要城市以及北京及深圳尋找更多類似投資項目機會。<br />\n<br />\n中國內地物業發展\t<br />\n<br />\n港鐵公司現正於中國內地發展物業顧問及管理業務，現有7份物業管理合約，並就此訂立了新合約，為中國國內不同地區的高檔物業發展項目提供管理及顧問服務。於2006年，SOHO中國有限公司訂立了委託港鐵公司管理豪華寫字樓／商業發展項目的3份新的物業管理合約，有關物業均位於北京的中心商業區，包括SOHO尚都、建外SOHO第七期及朝外SOHO。於2007年上半年已就北京2個辦公室及商業發展項目簽署一份諒解備忘錄，一個位於光華路，另一個位於西單。港鐵公司亦就北京銀座Mall的經營及物業管理訂立了長期的租約，銀座Mall為一可租用面積達19,295平方米的購物中心，已於2007年1月啟用。[41][53]2011年8月19日港鐵首次奪得中國鐵路上蓋物業、以底價19.77億元（人民幣．下同），平均每平方米樓面地價9590元，投得的深圳龍華綫車廠一期，為深圳地鐵龍華車輛段上蓋港鐵．天頌，總樓面面積約221.9萬平方呎，其中住宅佔206.3萬平方呎，涉及1,700伙，在2015年4月開售，預計在2016年落成，地價約19.77億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n至於與天津市地下鐵道集團合資發展的天津地鐵6號綫北運河站項目，亦會作綜合商住發展，涉及總樓面近300萬平方呎，較龍華綫車廠1期規模更大。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵副行政總裁梁國權接受訪問就曾指出，計劃以香港的鐵路加物業模式進軍內地，除了北京、深圳及杭州之外，亦會在其他一綫城市物色拓展機會，將海外淨資產比例由現時的10%提升至15%。"},{"pid":"f349038732b6ff90196325b6f30f2f60604ddabe","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dbfede5885ab28b79652a1fecb425270bdb76b3","tid":1524541,"uid":120040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:30:47.000Z","msg":"一人一Post 洗爆連登時事台 Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：［901入機場］今日重演721，黑警太子版核爆！唔使講野，入機場哂冷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與其死係街頭，不如死係機場<br />\n與其街頭食彈，不如機場食彈<br />\n與其被打爆頭，不如機場爆頭<br />\n與其被打爆眼，不如機場爆眼<br />\n與其黨鐵被打，不如機鐵被打<br />\n臥底鐘意燒街，不如燒機場啦<br />\n<br />\n攬炒機場！塞爆佢，唔使講野！<br />\n901無限期塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n見者Copy內容開新Post洗版，唔開Post自己檢討一下良心仲係唔係到！<br />\n<br />\n和理非出動嘅時候到了 你唔係忍到今日手足為你犧牲呀?"},{"pid":"2e46261940bb989830d46b88a36a1309412298bc","tid":1524541,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:21.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70semYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=bc4956c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70semYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=d549036d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70semYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=2249eea8\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"40b2c9be2aeb473fb8affddc60271bbc70a1cd33","tid":1524541,"uid":201574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:22.000Z","msg":"遲到好過冇到 今日開始要靠大家制裁黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101e04855cd00b62136c5cb7f9cb3628ea43f201","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎港豬錢益共産黨"},{"pid":"aca34c2b3efce640843f386c9a05ab9049633eb5","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拎港豬錢益共産黨"},{"pid":"4c96e5b969b6a4e40511a36f13778b5bf4d3ede9","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:33:04.000Z","msg":"賣港精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港始終有你"},{"pid":"5b57a145bf7bf0834324a9424dd1dc6f809853b8","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:33:43.000Z","msg":"港鐵係洪水猛獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049748fac87c81ab2378767a720ba5bc0544eacc","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推啊屌<br />\n咪撚再咁on9"},{"pid":"92ee0442d5f6c0bc639ee224fd4cf1dd7474f8f1","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:35:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推啊屌<br />\n咪撚再咁on9"},{"pid":"d12bbf0b2d8fd9bf689174efbc85506c66b6f417","tid":1524541,"uid":261913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:35:18.000Z","msg":"都話左政府有75%港鐵股份<br />\n你班港豬幾時先識醒"},{"pid":"9ee2d9493d2189f6a30bfd14ae02f71c7385835c","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推啊"},{"pid":"a46fd90e95144079f6107ffd5d0a03a7e5cd2a56","tid":1524541,"uid":197535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:36:20.000Z","msg":"10號強風信號生效，港鐵暫停所有地面和架空路段的列車，以及輕鐵和港鐵巴士的服務，至於地底路段則維持有限度服務。港鐵表示，東鐵線、馬鞍山線、西鐵線、機場快線、東涌線及輕鐵多個露天路段均發現有塌樹及障礙物，影響路軌和架空電纜的安全運作，工程人員會在安全情況許可下趕赴現場處理，復修時間定必較預期長。<br />\n<br />\n金屬氦氣球玩具隨時變成鐵路炸彈。氦氣球會影響電纜運作，被港鐵列為違禁品，以往港鐵職員發現乘客持氦氣球進入港鐵範圍會即時沒收。但本報發現，近月港鐵職員防備鬆懈，乘客攜帶氦氣球入閘視而不見，鐵路範圍處處見到「鐵路炸彈」。專家警告，如氦氣球飄起觸到鐵路電纜，會引致電力短路，可能會引起小火，導致電力供應系統「跳掣」，引發交通大災難。"},{"pid":"be6ded5d4dcec857c4edfaad71c2a6cea9101df2","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:36:32.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"c8fd78b4d77509a4f084dd4637cca99bf24a852a","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:36:43.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"81fa659118a55c7ec7ae32a4571fefad83dd663c","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:36:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"efdefe9f07e8ea1a2cece16052cac3dd87d169bb","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:37:06.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"c7eeab14dd927490c4b5c4295ad192e8027c66c0","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"991a21fa2321ccea069d91ededc4dad24ac29efe","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"4591a2101a4e9952f9ad524f872798d3c659416c","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:37:39.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"eb66bbfcd39ae2623ac408683f31e3d2187a57c9","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:37:52.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ee8cb162f63d446b5f294ab6ff51a3c9fec4e95f","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:38:02.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"c00d869da2e5670fa47206cc8d0640e37c5bd173","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:38:17.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"00d626f6d117ba750256ffae6bb91abec9a26c04","tid":1524541,"uid":203508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"屌咪繼續搭車唔俾錢囉<br />\n又閪用咩<br />\n在乎你嗰少少錢咩"}]}